This Application contains two activities
The main activity takes the list of places from the server and displays it as a list view on the screen
If you click on one place you are directed to the second Activity to view the description of the selected place
To remove the selected place click the "-" button on the menu bar
To add a place enter all the place description values to be added in edit text field of each category and then press the "+" button. The place gets added to the server list and you can view the new added place in the MainActivity
To simply browse and return to the main screen press the 'Back' button in the second screen
To edit a place edit its category keeping same place name and press the "+" button